text: Audrey Rennard (born 14 January 1933) is a British gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
